snippet.title: COMPOUND in Early Access! V0.1.0
snippet.description:
More maps, more weapons, more enemies - more everything! Also featuring better controls and snap turning for Rift/Touch users.

Check out COMPOUND on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/615120/COMPOUND/
